---
name: Auth / login pipeline
category: Security
tags: [oauth, decision, secure-edge]
description: Demonstrates the secure edge kind for sensitive flows and decision diamonds for branching.
---
# Auth / login pipeline

nodes:
  - id: user,  kind: actor,    label: User
  - id: login, kind: service,  label: "Login API"
  - id: auth,  kind: auth,     label: OAuth
  - id: check, kind: decision, shape: diamond, label: "Valid?"
  - id: home,  kind: service,  label: Dashboard
  - id: deny,  kind: stop,     shape: pill, label: Deny

edges:
  - user  -> login, kind: secure, label: "creds"
  - login -> auth,  kind: secure, label: "verify"
  - auth  -> check
  - check -> home,  label: "yes"
  - check -> deny,  kind: error,  label: "no"
